<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Hillsborough Community College</h2>
<strong>Tampa, FL</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>HCC awards college credit for scores of 3, 4, or 5 on the College Board Advanced Placement Program examinations given at high schools each May. Once credit is awarded, the student may not repeat the course for a letter grade. No credit will be awarded to students who have previously been awarded CLEP or regular college credit for the same course.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.hccfl.edu/sacs/draft_report/cs3_4_4.htm" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

